<p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">2023年11月3日下午，运动场上旗帜飘扬，历时两天的江西软件职业技术大学第十八届运动会圆满落下帷幕。</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">这场师生联欢的盛会，让所有人都能挥洒恣意的热血。两天的时光，我们收获了荣耀，感受到了温情，也见证了热爱与拼搏。</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px;">各位运动健儿也取得了佳绩：</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704793252258010008.png" title="1704793252258010008.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704793262716095838.png" title="1704793262716095838.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704793284221030418.png" title="1704793284221030418.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:16px">&nbsp;<img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704793299792069086.png" title="1704793299792069086.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">自由角逐，奋力拼搏。以激情之名，让热血重燃。此次运动会，实现了运动成绩和精神文明的双丰收，以下经济管理学院的获奖奖项：</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">打破纪录</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">女子800米</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">B200503 万志乐</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">女子4*100接力赛</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">万志乐 饶蕾蕾 徐若涵 贺彬彬</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">获奖名单</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704793308127045828.png" title="1704793308127045828.png" alt="image.png"/><br/><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704793321136088047.png" title="1704793321136088047.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p style=";text-indent: 31px;padding: 0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">运动会让我们心心相融，与梦相拥，在相伴相知中增进情感，在拼搏奋进中追逐梦想。赛会迎来尾声，愿同学们能延续更高、更快、更强的体育精神，在学习与生活的赛道上不断展现自己的担当与勇气，热情与友好，光芒与自信，属于你们的青春才刚刚开始绽放！</span></p><p><br/></p>